Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a copy of this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Yamamoto-san also reads poetry books...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, hurry up and give it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's hurry up and go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lunch counter's gonna get crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:22.81,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:28.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:34.90,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:40.87,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:48.25,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:52.96,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:58.88,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:07.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:12.69,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:19.82,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:26.58,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:22.81,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:28.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:34.90,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:40.87,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:48.25,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:52.96,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:58.88,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:07.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:12.69,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:19.82,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:26.58,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:40.76,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\fscx103.75\fscy100\pos(152,384)}Episode 10 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:41.05,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Yamamoto-san's upset, since she lost the picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get it back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't find the right time to talk to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You also had a copy of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why Yamamoto-san had a picture of Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... someone just went to throw the trash in the incinerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen to this! You won't believe what he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just spill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your English homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? You need to do it yourself sometimes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm... getting jealous again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because of that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan, is something bugging you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you haven't been able to relax all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But remember, no secrets between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair... with just one smile, I'll let you do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and take my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be called on today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want him all to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That picture... wasn't of Yano. It was picture of Yamamoto-san's sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! It all connects now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense for Yamamoto-san to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do the English assignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it down pat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.62,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.12,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,My English notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan's notebook is only for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some sort of harassment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my notebook before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Was there maybe.. a picture in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... never mind. If you didn't see it, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave it back to Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... did Yamamoto-san say anything about it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, nothing like "where'd you find it" or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan... why'd you have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really mad at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snooping around in other people's things is pretty awful, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:08:06.75,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanairo no niji ga koi no yukue shitteru no
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:18.68,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiseki wa meguru to miageta yozora wa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:30.11,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakomare maboshi kumo no ue de odoru
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:43.12,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikibasho wo sagashita tameiki ga irodzuku
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:55.26,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ushinau sono mae ni furete hashiri
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:09:07.27,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa tenohira nukumori de
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:19.41,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanasanaide mou sukoshi dake kowaresou yo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:25.58,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro yurete namida tte ochiru
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:31.71,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata no kao wa shizuka ni
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:38.30,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirakira ni terasou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:58.28,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi no sono mae no sono hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:04.87,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaze ni utau yume no hito
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:17.05,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayou kibun utare omoidaseta nara
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:29.06,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hohoemu sono tabi ni setsunasa tsumoru
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:34.23,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mabushii sora no naka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:08:06.75,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The seven-colored rainbow knows where our love is headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:18.68,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,As the seasons turn, the night sky I gaze up at
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:30.11,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,surrounds me, and illusions dance above the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:43.12,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to find where it led, but it only colored my sighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:55.26,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to reach out and touch it before it fades away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:09:07.27,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The palm of your hand is filled with warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:19.41,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let go just yet. Everything seems about to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:25.58,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,As my heart wavers, tears fall from my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:31.71,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face in my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:38.30,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,twinkles brightly and silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:58.28,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes before me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:04.87,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,sing in the wind of the one I dream of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:17.05,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm lost, I feel really down, and when I think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:29.06,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time you smile, the pain piles up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:34.23,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,In the blinding sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you working ten pages ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing else to do at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing else to do, so you study?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate me that much, we shouldn't have even gotten to know each other to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only used me to get revenge on my sister, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Revenge"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't mean anything, and I'd have no reason to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see yours, Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, you're not gonna buy those clothes you just tried on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They looked so good on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you invite me to go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a fight with Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Yano doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pretty awful..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't really snooping around...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano can be really cold sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't called me, even though it's Sunday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello---
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you! Are you Yano's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the same middle school as Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at Take's house right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's throwing him a birthday party today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... sure... but I'm out shopping with a friend right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend?! Is she female?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great! Bring her with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make a whole hook-up party out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, is your friend cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing with my cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I was thinking of making a hook-up party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Ya--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He hung up on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... just snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you really came?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat, heave a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That annoyed look was blatantly obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you have to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have everything, since he runs a liquor store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding, just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you sit next to Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no... here's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting kinda tired. Maybe I should head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that little... he's ignoring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For being my boyfriend, he's really ruining things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought coming empty-handed might seem rude, so I bought you a present, Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, don't mention it. It's nothing special, so, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cellphone strap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.89,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Sea Urchin-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I told you it wasn't anything special...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I was going for a gag gift, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a bit too corny...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I think I actually kinda like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a really hard time choosing, so that's great to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Cheers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too transparent, Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... let's try to nonchalantly change the topic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it's that, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, yeah! It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the season for sea urchins, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't change the topic one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take! Take!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going with the topic change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you always do! You're good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea urchins?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jealous of the sea urchin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're jealous, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had such a bored look on your face this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not jealous at all of that weird strap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you find a different look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my birthday, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sympathizing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting such a lame sea urchin like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just pitiful, getting so happy over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? You're obviously just jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... be an adult about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing away someone's present like that... you're scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world doesn't revolve around you, Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my sea urchin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to take me home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying. Go away, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world may not revolve around me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you're here for me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you just did was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that sort of stuff, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything that won't be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Yano can be cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you don't need me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong with you being unable to believe in people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever believed in someone and been betrayed by them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you're not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you throw it out the window...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I threw a peanut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I got jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It annoys me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said it was weird and lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, I want one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't deny it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to Takeuchi sometime when I'm not watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask for something else out of selfishness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be nice to any other guys when I'm around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if you're not looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, I know you don't want to, but please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to read between the lines here. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The starry sky looks just like the planetarium...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a shooting star whizzed by, what would you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I wish to become rich as soon as possible."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't talk about unrealistic dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wish to marry Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wish to be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd wish to be your first and your last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always attach that stuff to what I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you say that pretty easily, but do you know what it really means?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be together with you until you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you swear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it on the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a shooting star, I wish to be with Nana-chan forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't seem to find the sea urchin anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked for it all night, but I couldn't find it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano only pretended to throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've told you sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm just glad I didn't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:21:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but I won't put it on my cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd probably get the wrong idea if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm really sorry about this, and for making you have to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun is... Takeuchi-kun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's squeezing in delight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if Yano tried taking some pointers from Takeuchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when you keep flirting like this, it's hard to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kind of like my boy cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's only five, but he always gets in my shirt and hugs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perverted little runt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that. He just want to touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I carry him around, he gets really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's only happy if a girl does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the three-year-old girl doesn't do that at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm the same as a five-year-old brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder If I hurt his pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about. It's just me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a hug, so why don't you come on over?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, he really is the same as a five-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some girl from school is waiting outside for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's here to confess her love?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of pisses me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it kinda looks like he's used to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back in a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why Onee-chan was riding...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in Kagawa's car that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:23:04.69,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Taisetsu na anata no hitomi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:12.03,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi wa utsutteru no ka na
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:23.00,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Komorebi sashikomu madobe ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:30.72,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite yashiku nareru darou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:37.48,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro kakushite kodou kakushite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:39.77,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsumo no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:46.15,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakariaenai tsurasa ga tamaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:55.41,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Waraitai waraitai kokoro no mannaka de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:59.91,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ni wa uchiakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:04.67,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogaru watashi yowaki na watashi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:06.92,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinou no hanashi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:10.17,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,dou demo ii koto mo zenbu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.17,0:24:15.01,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Aishiteru kore kara mo zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:21.60,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yde wo kunde asuite ikou Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.78,0:24:41.50,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisetsu wa watashi dake nokoshite
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.50,0:24:48.25,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Taisetsu na hito tsurete yukun da ne
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.26,0:24:55.89,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi wo sagashite kimi wo sagashite
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.89,0:25:02.14,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna toki demo kimi wo sagashiteiru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.14,0:25:07.40,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsukaru no sore wa kimi na no?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:13.78,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanashikute kanashikute
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.78,0:25:18.41,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,nakidashisou ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.41,0:25:27.00,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Dore dake no omoi nara dakishimete kureru no?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.00,0:25:32.30,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah waraitai waraitai
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.30,0:25:34.26,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanimokamo nage...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:23:04.69,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm reflected
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:12.03,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,in your precious eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:23.00,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how I can always be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:30.72,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,on the windowsill where the sunshine always falls?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:37.48,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I hide my true feelings and the thumping of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:39.77,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,As always,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:46.15,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,the pain of not being able to understand each other burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:55.41,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to smile, I want to smile, down to the core of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:59.91,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:04.67,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,about how I pretend to be strong, about how I'm weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:06.92,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,about what happened yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:10.17,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,about everything that means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.17,0:24:15.01,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue to love you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:21.60,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my arm and let's walk. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.78,0:24:41.50,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The seasons leave only me behind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.50,0:24:48.25,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and take my precious person away, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.26,0:24:55.89,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I look for you, I look for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.89,0:25:02.14,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always looking for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.14,0:25:07.40,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I find that person, is it really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:13.78,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sad, I'm so sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.78,0:25:18.41,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,I could cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.41,0:25:27.00,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,How much feeling must I give to be able to embrace you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.00,0:25:32.30,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I want to smile, I want to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.30,0:25:34.26,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.91,0:25:34.93,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\fscx103.75\fscy122.5\pos(432,377)}Episode 11 Preview...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.61,0:25:11.11,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,You... haven't forgotten\N about Onee-chan at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.69,0:25:16.32,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed both \Nme and her at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.32,0:25:19.20,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going the\N way you want it to, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.83,0:25:21.25,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied \Nwith yourself now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.25,0:25:22.87,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.87,0:25:26.00,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, more than\N anyone else in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.00,0:25:29.59,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, Yano... talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.59,0:25:32.13,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.13,0:25:33.80,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll accept it.
